Yeh to masjid he
Pak jagah he

Aur jab taq shiyashat masjid ke andar thi ne tab taq shiyashat vaju karke ki jati thi aur quran ko samne rakh ke ki jati thi

Aur jab masjid se nikal kar alayda kacheri me aagayi ne tab se vaju karke b bandh ho gayi aur adal hona bi band ho gaya

Aaj to adalat me adal ho nahi raha

Log paiso kaa galat ishtemal karke adal hone nahi dete

Kya nabi e pak ne koi alag adalat banayi thi??

Kya abubakar shiddiq ne alag adalat banayi thi??

Kya umar farooq ne alag adalat banayi thi??

Kya usmane gani ne alag adalat banayi thi??

Kya maula ali ne alag adalat banayi thi??

Yeh sabne masjid me hi to adal kiya he

Kya inke  jaisa koi adal kar shakta he bhala??

Umar e farooq ne jitna adal kiya utna koi kar shakta he bhala

Ala hazrat ne court ko kabhi adalat nahi kaha

Voh kahete the adalat use kahete he jaha adal ho

Yeh to kacheri he

And when I entered the mosque, I started praying and kept the Quran in front of me.

And when she came out of the mosque and came to the court, then she was tied up and the court was tied up.

Today there is no justice in the court

People don't let money get corrected by misusing it.

tell me something

Did the Prophet and then create any separate court??

Did Abubakar Shiddiq create a separate court??

Did Umar Farooq create a separate court??

Did the Ottoman woman create a separate court??

Did Maula Ali create a separate court??

He has done this to everyone in the mosque.

Is he capable of doing anything like this??

The more Umar and Farooq acted, the more they could do, he said.

Ala Hazrat never called the court a court.

He says he uses the court where justice is done.
